text: Madoka, is there anything troubling you?

I see.
If there's anything, feel free to consult me anytime.

Hey, look,  Madoka!
There seems to be something interesting over there.

Is it an old shopping street?
There's a flashy arcade, but...
Yeah, most of the shops are closed too.

It's like a ghost town...
It must have been much livelier in the past.
